reviewText: Good for a virgin to watch and learn only
This is very good because it is about couples in love, making love.  It is not porn!  YAY!  My Lover and I really enjoy watching their things!
Wish I could get a refund.  This DVD defies description it's so bad.  It's old, 70-80's, poorly scripted, awkward love scenes, no good stuff.  Rent a cable movie instead. Save your dollars!
